title: prostitute_pre
---
<<set $context = "transactional">>

She leans against the wall, watching you with practiced ease.

-> $c2: "How much?"
    <<set $tone = "direct">>
    <<jump prostitute_start>>

-> $c2: "You look tired."
    <<set $tone = "empathetic">>
    <<jump prostitute_start>>

-> $c2: "Just... want company."
    <<set $tone = "uncertain">>
    <<jump prostitute_start>>
===

title: prostitute_start
---
She studies you for a moment, then nods.

<<fade_out>>
<<jump prostitute_act>>
===

title: prostitute_act
---
The room is quiet. Close. Breathing, movement, small reactions.

-> $c2: Follow her lead
    <<set $sync += 1>>
    <<set $presence += 0>>
    "You let her guide the pace."

-> $c2: Try to control the rhythm
    <<set $sync -= 1>>
    <<set $presence += 0>>
    "You push forward, slightly out of step."

-> $c2: Slow down, watch her face
    <<set $sync += 0>>
    <<set $presence += 1>>
    "You pay attention to the subtle shifts in her expression."

-> $c2: Ask if she's okay
    <<set $sync += 0>>
    <<set $presence += 2>>
    "She seems surprised for a moment."

===

title: prostitute_post
---
<<fade_in>>

She gets dressed quickly.

-> $c2: Leave without a word
    <<set $emotional_outcome -= 1>>
    "She doesn't look at you."

-> $c2: Thank her politely
    <<set $emotional_outcome += 0>>
    "She nods. Professional."

-> $c2: Ask if she's really okay
    <<set $emotional_outcome += 1>>
    "She hesitates. Something genuine, briefly."

===
